Comment: Derivative composite of (a) the Bayerische Staatsbibliothek Munich
 scan of Olaus Magnus's 1539 Carta Marina (public domain), and (b) a
 20th-century colored facsimile reference held by the James Ford Bell
 Library at the University of Minnesota and accessed via Google Arts &
 Culture. Compositing, tonal/color adjustment, and final crop by Hat Labs
 Ltd, 2026.

